\c 11
\s UJeremiya lesivumelwano
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi elafika kuJeremiya livela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lisithi:
\v 2 Zwanini amazwi\x + 11.6,8. 2 Kho. 23.3.\x* alesisivumelwano,\x + 11.6,8. 2 Kho. 23.3.\x* likhulume ebantwini bakoJuda lakubahlali beJerusalema.
\v 3 Njalo uthi kibo: Itsho njalo IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Uqalekisiwe umuntu ongalaleli amazwi alesisivumelwano,\x + Dute. 27.26. Gal. 3.10.\x*
\v 4 engawalayela oyihlo ngosuku engibakhupha ngalo elizweni leGibhithe, esithandweni sensimbi,\x + Dute. 4.20.\x* ngisithi: Lalelani ilizwi lami,\x + 7.22,23; 11.7. Levi 26.3,12.\x* liwenze njengakho konke engililaya khona; ngalokho lizakuba ngabantu bami,\x + 7.22,23; 11.7. Levi 26.3,12.\x* lami ngibe nguNkulunkulu wenu,
\v 5 ukuze ngimise isifungo engasifunga kuboyihlo\x + Dute. 7.12,13. Hlab. 105.9,10.\x* ukuthi ngibanike ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju, njengalamuhla.\x + 32.22. Eks. 3.8.\x* Ngasengiphendula ngathi: Ameni, N\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Memezela wonke lamazwi emizini yakoJuda\x + 33.10.\x* lezitaladeni zeJerusalema, usithi: Zwanini amazwi alesisivumelwano,\x + 11.6,8. 2 Kho. 23.3.\x* liwenze.\x + Dute. 27.26. Gal. 3.10.\x*\x + 11.8. Roma 2.13. Jak. 1.22.\x*
\v 7 Ngoba ngafakaza lokufakaza kuboyihlo ngosuku engabakhuphula ngalo elizweni leGibhithe, kuze kube lamuhla, ngivuka ngovivi ngifakaza,\x + 2 Lan. 36.15.\x* ngisithi: Lalelani ilizwi lami.\x + 7.22,23; 11.7. Levi 26.3,12.\x*
\v 8 Kodwa kabalalelanga,\x + 34.14.\x* kababekanga indlebe yabo, kodwa bahamba, ngulowo lalowo ngobulukhuni benhliziyo yabo embi.\x + 3.17.\x* Ngakho ngizaletha phezu kwabo wonke amazwi alesisivumelwano,\x + 11.6,8. 2 Kho. 23.3.\x* engabalaya ukuthi ba\add w\add*enze,\x + 11.8. Roma 2.13. Jak. 1.22.\x* kodwa kaba\add w\add*enzanga.
\p
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Kutholakele ugobe phakathi kwabantu bakoJuda,\x + Hez. 22.25. Isa. 8.12. Hos. 6.9.\x* laphakathi kwabahlali beJerusalema.
\v 10 Sebebuyele eziphambekweni zabokhokho babo,\x + 17.23. Hlab. 79.8.\x* abala ukuzwa ilizwi lami; bona balandela abanye onkulunkulu ukuze babakhonze; indlu yakoIsrayeli lendlu yakoJuda zisephulile isivumelwano sami engasenza laboyise.\x + Dute. 31.16,20.\x*
\p
\v 11 Ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Khangela, ngizaletha okubi phezu kwabo, abangeke baphume kukho; lapho bekhala kimi,\x + 11.14. Zaga 1.28.\x* kangiyikubezwa.
\v 12 Khona imizi yakoJuda labahlali beJerusalema bezahamba bakhale kubonkulunkulu ababatshisela impepha, kodwa kabayikubasindisa lokubasindisa ngesikhathi sobubi babo.
\v 13 Ngoba \add njenge\add*nani lemizi yakho babe\add njalo\add* onkulunkulu bakho,\x + 2.28.\x* Juda, la\add njenge\add*nani lezitalada zeJerusalema limisile amalathi kulokhu okuyangisayo, amalathi okutshisela uBhali impepha.
\v 14 Ngakho wena ungabakhulekeli lababantu,\x + 7.16.\x* futhi ungabaphakamiseli ukukhala kumbe umkhuleko,\x + 7.16.\x* ngoba kangiyikuzwa ngesikhathi sokukhala kwabo kimi ngenxa yenhlupheko yabo.\x + 11.14. Zaga 1.28.\x*
\p
\v 15 Othandekayo wami\x + 12.7. Hlab. 60.5.\x* ulani\x + Hlab. 50.16. Isa. 1.11,12.\x* endlini yami, lokhu enze amanyala \add l\add*abanengi,\x + Hez. 16.25.\x* lenyama engcwele i\add si\add*yedlule kuwe yini?\x + 7.21. Hag. 2.12.\x* Lapho \add usenza\add* okubi, kulapho uthokoza.\x + Zaga 2.14.\x*
\v 16 IN\nd kosi\nd* yabiza ibizo lakho \add ngokuthi\add*: Isihlahla somhlwathi esiluhlaza esihle ngezithelo ezinhle;\x + Hlab. 52.8.\x* ngomsindo wenhlokomo enkulu izasithungela ngomlilo,\x + Hez. 1.24.\x* lengatsha zaso zephuke.\x + Roma 1.17.\x*
\v 17 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, eyakuhlanyelayo,\x + 2.21. Isa. 5.2.\x* ikhulumile okubi ngawe, ngenxa yobubi bendlu yakoIsrayeli lobendlu yakoJuda, abakwenzileyo bemelene labo ngokwabo ukungicunula ngokutshisela uBhali impepha.\x + 7.18.\x*
\s Icebo lokubulala uJeremiya
\p
\v 18 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasingazisa ukuthi ngazi; wasungitshengisa izenzo zabo.
\v 19 Kodwa mina nganginjengewundlu \add kumbe\add* inkabi kusiwa ekuhlatshweni;\x + Isa. 53.7. Isam. 5.6.\x* ngoba ngangingazi ukuthi baceba amacebo bemelene lami,\x + 18.18. Lilo 3.60,61.\x* \add besithi\add*: Asichithe isihlahla lesithelo saso;\x + Mat. 7.16,17.\x* asimqume asuke\x + Isa. 53.8.\x* elizweni labaphilayo,\x + Hlab. 27.13.\x* ukuze ibizo lakhe lingabe lisakhunjulwa.\x + Hlab. 83.4.\x*
\v 20 Kodwa, wena N\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, umahluleli olungileyo, ohlola izinso\x + 6.27.\x* lenhliziyo,\x + 1 Sam. 16.7.\x*\x + 17.10; 20.12. Hlab. 7.9.\x* kangibone impindiselo yakho kibo;\x + 15.15; 17.18; 20.12. Lilo 3.64.\x* ngoba ngembule udaba lwami kuwe.
\v 21 Ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* ngamadoda eAnathothi,\x + Josh. 21.18.\x* adinga impilo yakho,\x + 12.6. Mat. 13.57.\x* esithi: Ungaprofethi ngebizo leN\nd kosi\nd*,\x + Isa. 30.10.\x* ukuze ungafi ngesandla sethu.\x + Dute. 13.1-5.\x*
\v 22 Ngakho itsho njalo IN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla: Khangela, ngizawajezisa; amajaha azakufa ngenkemba, amadodana awo lamadodakazi awo azakufa ngendlala,
\v 23 njalo kakuyikuba lensali kuwo; ngoba ngizaletha okubi phezu kwamadoda\x + 23.12.\x* eAnathothi,\x + Josh. 21.18.\x* \add ngo\add*mnyaka wempindiselo yawo.\x + 23.12.\x*\x + 46.21; 48.44; 50.27,31. Luka 19.44.\x*